SET OPERATION

AIM:
Implement all the set operations which are UNION, INTERSECTION and MINUS

1. Create a table student with id,name and mark
2. Create a table alumni with id,name and mark
3. Insert values into student and alumni table
4. Display students present in both student and alumni table (duplicate not allowed) (union)
5. Display common from both the student and alumni (intersect)
6. Display student name in student table but not in alumni (minus)


